                <h2>Plastic Monitoring System</h2>
                <p>
                    Tracking plastic waste is crucial for tackling global pollution, yet comprehensive life-cycle monitoring systems are lacking. 
                    Current methods focus on limited stages, like waste management inputs and marine debris. We aim to bridge this gap with advanced tracking solutions, 
                    enabling targeted strategies to protect ecosystems and drive sustainable change.
                </p>
                <button onclick="window.location.href='https://nap.nationalacademies.org/read/26132/chapter/8';" class="btn_lrn">LEARN MORE</button>
