<section class="innovation_goals" id="innovation_goals">
    <h1 class="fading-title">FUTURE GOALS</h1>
    <p>
        To overcome the current limitations of our AI-based solution, future efforts will focus on enhancing the reliability, precision, and scalability of the system. 
        This includes improving UAS hardware to address issues like battery life and weather resilience, ensuring uninterrupted operations. 
        Advanced geospatial mapping techniques will be integrated to mitigate inaccuracies in metadata and enhance the quality of aerial surveys. Additionally, 
        upgrading the AI model to achieve higher accuracy in detecting, distinguishing, and enumerating plastic litter will be prioritized. 
        Future development will also explore combining UAS data with satellite imagery and ground-based observations to ensure comprehensive coverage. 
        By addressing these challenges, the solution aims to provide a more robust and efficient system for monitoring and restoring aquatic ecosystems, 
        further supporting global environmental preservation efforts.
    </p>
</section>